    "headline": "Robinhood Accelerates International Push. What It Is Launching in Europe, Canada, and Singapore.",
    "summary": "Robinhood  is expanding its toolkit for investors and its reach abroad.  On Wednesday, the company unveiled new AI cryptocurrency trading capabilities for U.S. customers, new perpetual futures contracts for European customers, and expansion efforts in Canada and Singapore.  Johann Kerbrat, general manager of crypto and international at Robinhood, says the initiatives are intended to broaden access to investment strategies and products to more customers in markets outside the U.S. “We want to extend this vision to the rest of the world,” Kerbrat tells Barron’s.",
